SCION is an implementation of SCXML in JavaScript. 

SCION-Java provides lightweight bindings to the SCION library for Java. This allows SCXML to easily be used in Java development.

Online documentation can be found here: http://jbeard4.github.com/SCION-Java/docs/com/inficon/scion/SCXML.html

For a basic usage example, see: https://github.com/jbeard4/SCION-Java/blob/master/test/TestSCXML.java
